						<div class="postbody">Gyromite is sort of like that, where the second controller moves parts of the level, though ultimately you're supposed to control that via the first controller making the screen flash to tell the robot to press the second controller (instead of just putting those buttons on controller 1).<br /><br />Mega Man 3 lets you super-jump if you hold a button on controller 2, though this isn't really gameplay.</div>

