					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Dian Shi Mali (the &quot;PUSH START TO RICH&quot; slot machine game) puts some bet buttons and the start button on the second controller because there aren't enough buttons on the first.<br /><br />Smash TV rotates both controllers 90 degrees to the right into the &quot;double fisted&quot; position, so that one Control Pad moves and the other fires.</div>

